{"tid":1699741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義士：何君堯蝦香港人，所以我好嬲，我要殺死佢","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T07:53:00.000Z","uid":78546,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"82808114a8e0f53b947dca56c8efe68b69f64423","tid":1699741,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"涉案無業男被控企圖謀殺罪，案件今在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。據了解，事發時被告用刀刺向何君堯的左胸，其後聲稱：「因為何君堯蝦香港人，所以我好嬲，我要殺死佢。」案件押後至明年2月3日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n#何君堯遇襲<br />\n【涉刀刺何君堯被控企圖謀殺　疑犯事後稱：我要殺死佢】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/32sHC7l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32sHC7l&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=29b641fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32sHC7l</a><br />\n【疑犯被控企圖謀殺　今粉嶺法院提堂】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pQ45h6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pQ45h6&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=1900c091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pQ45h6</a>"},{"pid":"5a6891fdeb24f7f4992be7b573920a31894dd4ce","tid":1699741,"uid":78546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:58:06.000Z","msg":"據了解，事發時何君堯正進行拉票活動，被告上前獻膠花，並稱想與何合照。其間被告涉從袋中取出一把總長度33厘米、刀鋒長20厘米的刀，刺向何的左胸，隨即遭在場人士制服。被告於警誡下稱：「因為何君堯蝦香港人，所以我好嬲，我要殺死佢。」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯出選區議會屯門樂翠區，同區參選人有民主黨的盧俊宇及無報稱政治聯繫的蔣靖雯。"},{"pid":"33bee1b80a65a5e982b9975dcc84c5dfaa55fa13","tid":1699741,"uid":78131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:01:11.000Z","msg":"其實係咪試水溫睇吓有幾多人割？<br />\n如果大大批和理非支持會點？<br />\n呢次會唔會係建制派打錯牌俾我地上？"},{"pid":"cd82338836742fcd998f012d4302589a340601ad","tid":1699741,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"我冇野講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50a13b02269292134f4a930a3d23033f1314420","tid":1699741,"uid":243011,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":6